cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.GT 

This paper deals with optimizing cache policies in a network setting, which involves aspects of networking, distributed computing, and optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves optimization problems, which could fall under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.IT (Information Theory). The use of utility maximization and cost minimization could also fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory).
